{"tid":576100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律拎] 有關酒牌 如果用貢茶式舖頭 賣手工啤酒需要酒牌?","createTime":"2018-02-28T15:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T16:48:31.000Z","uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"009b4599c13492a9b113f378a6ccfddc0339314b","tid":576100,"uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"依家酒牌既法例:<br />\n&quot;根據香港法例《應課稅品（酒類）規例》，任何處所、娛樂場所或公眾場合售賣酒類供在場人士飲用，必須持有酒牌。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我開間舖賣下小食, 同時又賣下手工啤酒 (依家好流行: <a href=\"http://www.adaymag.com/2016/02/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2F2016%2F02%2F2&d=GqVjSgWqrYFaTjc252JhqEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=383b8904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.adaymag.com/2016/02/2</a> ... ries-hong-kong.html)<br />\n咁樣以貢茶式手法去賣手工啤酒(客人買後一定在店外飲用) 需要酒牌?<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一定好賣過Ｄ台式茶, 打低D台式野, 建立本土手工啤品牌"},{"pid":"b9ec1fcde52cdbaab36821df1dc2dec2b414939e","tid":576100,"uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"應該放落邊個台? 學術台?"},{"pid":"f61d282bddfa81c780fb90c5b9a18ddc68a2fd9b","tid":576100,"uid":145769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"如果餐廳或酒吧形式比較易中招<br />\n如果你係便利店形式就問題不大<br />\n<br />\n你啲對手做硬你"},{"pid":"bc48b597610b0b68112783845cbf33a26e08fd50","tid":576100,"uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61d282bddfa81c780fb90c5b9a18ddc68a2fd9b","tid":576100,"uid":145769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"如果餐廳或酒吧形式比較易中招<br />\n如果你係便利店形式就問題不大<br />\n<br />\n你啲對手做硬你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"咩對手? 點做我?"},{"pid":"a741757824d0ff02d037dca5127286548569fc89","tid":576100,"uid":113040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"無提供坐位俾人坐低飲係唔洗酒牌喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd4c5df13af224f58a0b3d94ccd2a9653f69577","tid":576100,"uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a741757824d0ff02d037dca5127286548569fc89","tid":576100,"uid":113040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"無提供坐位俾人坐低飲係唔洗酒牌喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係做得喇, 等我入定貨先"},{"pid":"b0f044728aab67a6a7bbe4507ff259b6175f307c","tid":576100,"uid":85997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"香港而家有冇類似既生意做緊?"},{"pid":"1a86017d45bf0c1550ce676b69ab0e38607670e3","tid":576100,"uid":7679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"你當自己係零售舖頭咁賣唔駛酒牌㗎<br />\n同埋酒牌要有食牌先會拎到"},{"pid":"4040d62c2a866f52dc3a066f4a561f7cc786d9ed","tid":576100,"uid":59930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"預先有廠封好樽就一定得，當士多賣啤酒咁。<br />\n如果要店內加工再賣就唔知得唔得"},{"pid":"f1e62a8680919fa24a96dfd31a883ef1f5cc307d","tid":576100,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"無人係你店舖内飲洒就得<br />\n你常點賣賣咩酒都無人理"},{"pid":"daf737623e9e1f99d109692578064e5035b37d52","tid":576100,"uid":65263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140919/18871059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140919%2F18871059&d=GqVjSgWqrYFaTjc252JhqEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=875abd4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140919%2F18871059&h=835f3c62\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140919/18871059</a><br />\n可以參考下"}]}